===========================================================================
Actions, which we should perform before using zix editor.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Install compizconfig-settings-manager on Ubuntu, so we
can disable some shortcuts. 

- Alt-Space -> Go to Ubuntu -> Settings -> Keyboard -> Shortcuts -> Windows -> "Activate the window menu" [Disable]
- Alt-`     -> Go to compizconfig -> Desktop -> Ubuntu Unity Plugin -> Switcher -> "Key to flip through windows in the switcher" [Disable]
- Ctrl-Alt-S -> Go to Ubunty -> Settings -> Keyboard -> Shortcuts -> Windows -> "Toggle shaded state" [Disable]

